:::The Destrocons:::

::As they near the Trainer base, the Destrocons see the beams of energy 
coming toward them::
Ramjet: Careful guys!
Skywarp: Im always careful.
Dirge: Suuuuuuure-AHHHH
::An energy beam narrowly misses him::
Dirge: I'll be quiet now.
::They continue to maneuver around the energy beams, and while maneuvering, 
their guns flip out::
Ramjet: Alright, you remember what Cygnar said! Give 'em the pit!
::The the three all start firing their blasters at the Trainer base::
